---

<section class="py-16 bg-[#1c252e] border-t border-[#2d3748]">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
            
            <!-- Main Content (2 cols) -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-2 prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Your Ultimate Destination for Free Udemy Coupons</h2>
                
                <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-8">
                    CoursesWyn is dedicated to helping learners worldwide access premium education for free. We automatically aggregate and verify <strong>100% OFF Udemy coupons</strong> every single day. Whether you are looking to master Python, learn Digital Marketing, or start a path in Web Development, we have a free course for you.
                </p>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
                    <div class="bg-[#1c252e] p-6 rounded-2xl border border-[#2d3748] hover:border-green-500/50 transition-all">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="text-green-500 bg-green-500/10 p-1 rounded-lg">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                            </span>
                            Verified Daily
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Our bots and community verify thousands of coupons daily to ensure you don't waste time on expired deals.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-[#1c252e] p-6 rounded-2xl border border-[#2d3748] hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-all">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <span class="text-blue-500 bg-blue-500/10 p-1 rounded-lg">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
                            </span>
                            Premium Content
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                            Get access to the exact same courses sold for $100+ on Udemy, including lifetime access and completion certificates.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Popular Skills</h3>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-12">
                    {["Python", "React", "Java", "Docker", "AWS", "Excel", "Photoshop", "SEO", "Marketing"].map(tag => (
                        <a href={`/search?q=${tag}`} class="bg-[#1c252e] border border-[#2d3748] px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm text-gray-300 hover:text-white hover:border-green-500 hover:bg-[#1c252e] transition-all">
                            {tag}
                        </a>
                    ))}
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- FAQ Sidebar (1 col) -->
            <div class="lg:col-span-1">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <details class="group bg-[#1c252e] rounded-xl border border-[#2d3748] open:border-green-500/50 open:bg-[#242938] transition-all duration-300">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold cursor-pointer list-none p-5 text-gray-200 hover:text-white">
                            <span>How to redeem coupons?</span>
                            <span class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
                            </span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="text-gray-400 px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-[#1c252e]/50 pt-4 animate-fadeIn">
                            Click "Redeem" on any course card. You'll be redirected to Udemy with the code applied automatically at checkout.
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <details class="group bg-[#1c252e] rounded-xl border border-[#2d3748] open:border-green-500/50 open:bg-[#242938] transition-all duration-300">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold cursor-pointer list-none p-5 text-gray-200 hover:text-white">
                            <span>Are courses truly free?</span>
                            <span class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
                            </span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="text-gray-400 px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-[#1c252e]/50 pt-4 animate-fadeIn">
                            Yes! These are 100% OFF promotional codes from instructors. Once enrolled, you own the course forever.
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <details class="group bg-[#1c252e] rounded-xl border border-[#2d3748] open:border-green-500/50 open:bg-[#242938] transition-all duration-300">
                        <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold cursor-pointer list-none p-5 text-gray-200 hover:text-white">
                            <span>Do I get certificates?</span>
                            <span class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
                            </span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="text-gray-400 px-5 pb-5 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-[#1c252e]/50 pt-4 animate-fadeIn">
                            Yes. Enrollments via 100% OFF coupons are treated as paid enrollments by Udemy, so you earn a certificate upon completion.
                        </div>
                    </details>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>
</section>
